info.narration:
[
{It may appear to just be an ordinary grinder, but please be careful. Every Abnormality may not have a reason to exist, but they all have a will to persist.},
{Its force of suction is extremely powerful.},
{The music it lets out is said to be terribly beautiful.},
{One’s blood shall make wondrous chords, and one’s flesh shall make great harmonies.}
]

[
{$0 will not be set in motion if nobody is nearby.},
{Before #0 entered, not a single movement came from $0. },
{Prior to #0 entering the unit, $0 was nothing more than a shut-off machine.},
{If $0 happened to have a power switch, #0 may be a bit more comfortable working with it.}
]

[
{#0 works with $0 as cautiously as they can.},
{#0 must always be careful when working in this unit, as $0 could activate at any moment.},
{$0 gives no form of response or reaction to #0, as if it were digesting bits of flesh internally. }
{#0 tries to get the work with $0 done quickly while it is motionless.}
]

[
{It’s rather simple to figure out when $0 activates; just open its lid and check how much flesh it has digested.},
{#0 doesn’t have the guts to open up $0’s lid to its mechanical guts and check when it will next activate.},
{Rumor has it that any employee who opened $0’s lid later requested a sick leave.},
{In fact, $0’s insides are said to be sophisticated, but no employee dares to check it with their own eyes.}
]

[
{Today is #0’s lucky day; $0 hasn’t activated.},
{#0 is rather thankful that $0 is inactive, however, they give their best condolences to whichever employee will work with it next.},
{$0’s decided to take the day off.},
{$0 doesn’t respond as it is still finishing up its leftovers.}
]

[
{The Containment Unit fills with the unprecedented harmony that leaks from $0.},
{To give birth to the greatest masterpieces, sacrifices must be made. $0 is the perfect example of this phrase.},
{All that remains of #0 is a few pieces of flesh and bone, and their own composition that will never be heard again.}
]

[
{#0 has been possessed by the timbre of $0. They won’t respond to any commands.},
{#0 has fallen for the charms of $0’s transmundane song. Their mind is completely paralyzed.}
]

observe.desc:
[
{It takes the form of a long cuboid machine.}
]

[
{At first glance, all it seems to be is a simple industrial grinder. However, the existence of it having an individual “will” meets the criteria to be classified as an Abnormality.}
]

[
{When approached or touched, the employee will become delirious and throw themself into the Abnormality's mechanical body. Afterward, the machine's ventilation fan will quickly shut off, and the sound of the Abnormality operating can be heard from within. This process takes about 5 minutes.}
]

[
{After a few experiments, we have concluded that the Abnormality desires to gain "music" from this interaction.}
]

  [
  {<i>There is no detailed research into this Abnormality’s “music”, however, there is a hypothesis that it has a special characteristic that attracts humans in correlation to their specific behaviors or psychological counseling records. If one of our employees has been determined to be addicted to the music, they will need to be treated quickly to prevent any collateral damage.</i>}
]

